      "description": "Presenting an exceptional opportunity to acquire a vehicle maintained to an exacting standard. This specimen exhibits flawless aesthetics and mechanical integrity, reflective of its pristine provenance. Discerning buyers will appreciate the showroom-quality finish and the uncompromising performance of this investment-grade automobile. Available for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 44900.0,
